OL,3,CCouple jailed for #270,000 benefits
OL,4,Cfraud scheme
OL,6,FLloyd began her fraudulent activity in
OL,7,FFebruary 2012 by claiming housing
OL,8,Fbenefit from West Lancashire Borough
OL,9,FCouncil for a caravan she did not
OL,10,Fhave, prosecutors told the court.
OL,12,FShe even forged a tenancy agreement to
OL,13,Fsupport the lie, securing more than
OL,14,F#71,000.
OL,16,FFrom 2018, she expanded her scam to
OL,17,Finclude false claims to St Helens
OL,18,FBorough Council, stating Phillips
OL,19,Fneeded extensive care.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
