OL,3,CCouple jailed for #270,000 benefits
OL,4,Cfraud scheme
OL,6,FShe posed as his sister using Zoe
OL,7,FPhillips' birth certificate, and
OL,8,Fclaimed that she herself was not
OL,9,Fworking due to caring for Phillips 35
OL,10,Fhours a week.
OL,12,FBut in reality, she held two jobs
OL,13,Funder false names: "Wendy Lloyd" at a
OL,14,Fcare agency and "Angela Valentine" at
OL,15,FTesco.
OL,17,FLloyd received more than #73,000 in
OL,18,Fpayments related to non-existent
OL,19,Fcarers, and an additional #753 in
OL,20,Fcarer's allowance.
