OL,3,CCouple jailed for #270,000 benefits
OL,4,Cfraud scheme
OL,6,FIn 2022, she falsely claimed her son
OL,7,Fhad serious medical issues, using the
OL,8,Fidentity of the late Joyce Bibby as
OL,9,Fhis supposed carer.
OL,11,FHer lie allowed her to claim nearly
OL,12,F#10,000 in disability living allowance
OL,13,Fand more than #500 in personal
OL,14,Findependence payments (pip).
OL,16,FShe also used the same deceased
OL,17,Fwoman's identity to claim more than
OL,18,F#13,500 in benefits for her own
OL,19,Fsupposed care needs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
