OL,3,CCouple jailed for #270,000 benefits
OL,4,Cfraud scheme
OL,6,FPhillips helped himself to #100,980 in
OL,7,Ffalse claims for employment support
OL,8,Fallowance, pip, housing benefit and
OL,9,Fcouncil tax reduction over a period of
OL,10,Faround five-and-a-half years from
OL,11,FApril 2018 onwards.
OL,13,FHe failed to report that Lloyd had
OL,14,Fmoved in with him, allowing him to
OL,15,Fclaim more than #13,000 in housing
OL,16,Fbenefits and nearly #2,300 in council
OL,17,Ftax relief as if he were living alone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
